> left completely obscured.

Try this:

DestroyFunc	Raise-and-Focus
AddToFunc	Raise-and-Focus \
  "I"		Raise
+ "I"		Focus

Key F1	A	N	Next [!iconic CurrentDesk] Raise-and-Focus
Key F2	A	N	Prev [!iconic CurrentDesk] Raise-and-Focus


