> I will also try out the FvwmEvent solution. BTW, is there any way to make the
> pager looks like multiple desktops, but just having one desk with many
> virtual screens? I like the idea of having seperate desktops for different
> stuff such as Mail, Web, Work etc... But due to this mozilla bug, I probably
